<subSubSection id="25A5D896F3A6438B58263F41AB066CD4" pageId="0" pageNumber="119" type="nomenclature">
<paragraph id="0276C9136A8B6EC94256C8B3428779DB" pageId="0" pageNumber="119">
Genus 
<taxonomicName id="52ECCC0FB5FD0ADBC4B6E66BD796605B" LSID="BF9E287B-87EC-53CD-B60E-F97B1EF45E35" authority="Bamber, 1997" authorityName="Bamber" authorityYear="1997" class="Malacostraca" family="Parapseudidae" genus="Swireapseudes" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Swireapseudes" order="Tanaidacea" pageId="0" pageNumber="119" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Swireapseudes Bamber, 1997</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="8EEE9B63101A5612D080DFBDEA674C3B" pageId="0" pageNumber="119" type="type species">
<paragraph id="F6B4BE6F020919E570BFAE031F1272A3" pageId="0" pageNumber="119">Type species.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="4B1BBD7F82C1B41D8345556CA6157AD6" pageId="0" pageNumber="119">
<taxonomicName id="7A19156FA604E993B837CD680DBA6506" authorityName="Bamber" authorityYear="1997" class="Malacostraca" family="Apseudidae" genus="Swireapseudes" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Swireapseudes toloensis" order="Tanaidacea" pageId="0" pageNumber="119" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="toloensis">
<emphasis id="B80345AD2FC18592B60BBAD5ABAE954A" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="119">Swireapseudes toloensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Bamber, 1997
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="814FA4EB13F96CAE4FEF044639B638EC" pageId="0" pageNumber="119" type="remarks">
<paragraph id="216F3FCF4F678CEB60447AC41F269504" pageId="0" pageNumber="119">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="50AF538C97518741C5AD76BA58A31B74" pageId="0" pageNumber="119">
This genus has once been synonymised with 
<taxonomicName id="6C7134545BBA80F89D3A21C9DC959F2C" authorityName="Bacescu" authorityYear="1978" class="Malacostraca" family="Parapseudidae" genus="Pakistanapseudes" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Pakistanapseudes" order="Tanaidacea" pageId="0" pageNumber="119" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="A13BA30402F177976EDF3605918E1E8A" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="119">Pakistanapseudes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation id="89325A51855D57EC79D25F0A4404A707" author="Bamber, RN" editor="Morton, B" journalOrPublisher="Proceedings of an International Workshop Reunion Conference. Hong Kong, 21 - 26 October 2001 Hong Kong University Press, Hong Kong" pageId="0" pageNumber="119" pagination="167 - 194" refId="B6" refString="Bamber, RN, Sheader, M, 2003. A reinterpretation of the taxonomy and zoogeography of Pakistanapseudes and Swireapseudes (Crustacea: Tanaidacea): Hong Kong taxa in the world context. In: Morton, B, Ed., Perspectives on Marine Environment Change in Hong Kong and Southern China, 1977-2001. Proceedings of an International Workshop Reunion Conference. Hong Kong, 21-26 October 2001 Hong Kong University Press, Hong Kong: 167 - 194" title="A reinterpretation of the taxonomy and zoogeography of Pakistanapseudes and Swireapseudes (Crustacea: Tanaidacea): Hong Kong taxa in the world context." volumeTitle="Perspectives on Marine Environment Change in Hong Kong and Southern China, 1977 - 2001." year="2003">Bamber and Sheader (2003)</bibRefCitation>
but revalidated by 
<bibRefCitation id="D89A9611633CB0B09C912D12B9C76B2C" author="Gutu, M" journalOrPublisher="Curtea Veche, Bucharest, Romania" pageId="0" pageNumber="119" refId="B12" refString="Gutu, M, 2006. New Apseudomorph Taxa (Crustacea, Tanaidacea) of the World Ocean. Curtea Veche, Bucharest, Romania" title="New Apseudomorph Taxa (Crustacea, Tanaidacea) of the World Ocean." year="2006">
<normalizedToken id="4C819AA591C4E19E525C1E11463A1BD8" originalValue="Guţu">Gutu</normalizedToken>
(2006)
</bibRefCitation>
. The main morphological features that distinguish these two genera are: 1) the presence of ventrodistal prolongation on pereopods 2, 3, 5 and 6 in species of 
<taxonomicName id="6ABF69A4DD0BFC5298DBD450F50CB88F" authorityName="Bamber" authorityYear="1997" class="Malacostraca" family="Apseudidae" genus="Swireapseudes" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Swireapseudes" order="Tanaidacea" pageId="0" pageNumber="119" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="C38F3391F979079B9BB1B608F24777F3" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="119">Swireapseudes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, compared to the presence of a ventrodistal prolongation on pereopods 2 and 3 in some species of 
<taxonomicName id="D19D1686F26C8D2303C5E8EBA224F622" authorityName="Bacescu" authorityYear="1978" class="Malacostraca" family="Parapseudidae" genus="Pakistanapseudes" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Pakistanapseudes" order="Tanaidacea" pageId="0" pageNumber="119" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="6A3F83F40F5D1FAC5A19FE67EA89D8F3" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="119">Pakistanapseudes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
but never on pereopods 5 and 6; 2) the presence of sexual dimorphism of cheliped in species of 
<taxonomicName id="C5D3B781C4490E78C1516B1AF017671A" authorityName="Bamber" authorityYear="1997" class="Malacostraca" family="Apseudidae" genus="Swireapseudes" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Swireapseudes" order="Tanaidacea" pageId="0" pageNumber="119" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="06549CBD3CD1F77C1C655488C929D042" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="119">Swireapseudes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<bibRefCitation id="6BACC35B5FF41F664CE0317A8CD07149" author="Gutu, M" journalOrPublisher="Grigore Antipa" pageId="0" pageNumber="119" pagination="43 - 70" refId="B13" refString="Gutu, M, 2008. A revision of the family Parapseudidae, with description of a new tribe and three genera. The diagnoses and the key of the superspecific taxa (Crustacea: Tanaidacea: Apseudomorpha). Travaux du Museum National d'Histoire naturelle. Grigore Antipa 51: 43 - 70" title="A revision of the family Parapseudidae, with description of a new tribe and three genera. The diagnoses and the key of the superspecific taxa (Crustacea: Tanaidacea: Apseudomorpha). Travaux du Museum National d'Histoire naturelle." volume="51" year="2008">
<normalizedToken id="73417C91A71B837D207AA88E282ED030" originalValue="Guţu">Gutu</normalizedToken>
2008
</bibRefCitation>
). Two species of 
<taxonomicName id="72939F7C0C6C385B7BD3C4A49CE1B60B" authorityName="Bamber" authorityYear="1997" class="Malacostraca" family="Apseudidae" genus="Swireapseudes" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Swireapseudes" order="Tanaidacea" pageId="0" pageNumber="119" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="7F363FA6745CE26C966A72879F740CA0" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="119">Swireapseudes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
have been previously recorded at very distant locations: 
<taxonomicName id="D0135D1BDD24C510AFA70D68AE0B1BA5" authorityName="Gutu &amp; Iliffe" authorityYear="2008" class="Malacostraca" family="Apseudidae" genus="Swireapseudes" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Swireapseudes birdi" order="Tanaidacea" pageId="0" pageNumber="119" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="birdi">
<emphasis id="96D0D0F3DC78D8BF9BAA59E1604D0D85" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="119">Swireapseudes birdi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken id="FDF1354C92A248010CCCA0EB2F630408" originalValue="Guţu">Gutu</normalizedToken>
&amp; Iliffe, 2008 (Eleuthera Island, Bahamas) and 
<taxonomicName id="B9A27605A3B0F1A9B615CEF7F6E48543" authorityName="Bamber" authorityYear="1997" class="Malacostraca" family="Apseudidae" genus="Swireapseudes" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Swireapseudes toloensis" order="Tanaidacea" pageId="0" pageNumber="119" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="toloensis">
<emphasis id="0E3C1A993A6B98EA8E35990ED8B3CD69" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="119">Swireapseudes toloensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Bamber, 1997 (Tolo Channel, Hong Kong).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
